1. *Predstavljam* svoju novu kolekciju na modnoj reviji. (I am presenting my new collection at a fashion show.)
2. Oni *predstavljaju* vladu Srbije u pregovorima sa EU. (They represent the Serbian government in negotiations with the EU.)
3. Nisam siguran kako da *predstavim* sebe na intervjuu za posao. (I'm not sure how to introduce myself at a job interview.)
4. Kada *predstavljaš* neku ideju, važno je da budeš ubedljiv. (When presenting an idea, it's important to be persuasive.)
5. Uloga glumca je da *predstavi* lik na način da ga publika shvati. (The role of an actor is to portray a character in a way that the audience understands.)
6. *Predstavili* smo svoj projekat na konferenciji, ali nismo dobili dovoljno podrške. (We presented our project at the conference, but we didn't get enough support.)
7. Kao novi direktor, moraću da *se predstavim* zaposlenima u kompaniji. (As the new director, I will have to introduce myself to the employees in the company.)
8. Njegov govor je *predstavljao* inspiraciju za sve prisutne na konferenciji. (His speech was an inspiration for everyone present at the conference.)